{"lang": "zh_TW", "eventid": "act28side", "eventName": "不義之財", "entryType": "ACTIVITY", "storyCode": "CV-5", "avgTag": "行動後", "storyName": "疑惑之影", "storyInfo": "黑鋼聯合當地銀行接連不斷地驅逐負債居民離開地塊，潔西卡感到憤怒的同時也深覺無力，而伍德洛也在夜晚時分找上了“橋夾”克里夫。\n", "storyList": [{"id": 0, "prop": "HEADER", "attributes": {"key": "title_test", "is_skippable": "true", "fit_mode": "BLACK_MASK"}}, {"id": 1, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 2, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 3, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 4, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 5, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "42_g4_bank", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 6, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$distressed_intro", "key": "$distressed_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 7, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 8, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 9, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1039_1#1$1", "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 10, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 11, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1039_1#3$1"}}, {"id": 12, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……都這麼晚了，怎麼外面還有人。", "name": "西爾維婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1039_1#3$1"}, {"id": 13, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 14, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 15, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1039_1#6$1"}}, {"id": 16, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那是……潔西卡小姐？", "name": "西爾維婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1039_1#6$1"}, {"id": 17, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 18, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 19, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 20, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_1034_jesca2_1#9$1"}}, {"id": 21, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "42_g7_sonwydowntown_n", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 22, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 23, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 24, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "name": "avg_npc_1039_1#1$1", "posfrom": "-150,0", "posto": "0,0", "duration": 0.8}}, {"id": 25, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 26, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "name": "avg_npc_1039_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 27, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "潔西卡小姐，你這個時候來銀行做什麼？", "name": "西爾維婭"}}, {"id": 28, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_1034_jesca2_1#10$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 29, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我……呼、呼……我有事想找你們！", "name": "潔西卡"}, "figure_art": "avg_1034_jesca2_1#10$1"}, {"id": 30, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "name": "avg_npc_1039_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 31, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "至、至少……進來再說吧。", "name": "西爾維婭"}}, {"id": 32, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 33, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 34, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 35, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "42_g4_bank", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 36, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 37, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 38, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_higheldshosfts", "volume": 0.5}}, {"id": 39, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1041_1#1$1", "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 40, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 41, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "西爾維婭，怎麼回事？我不是說了晚上不要打開大門嗎，這幾天黑鋼的人在外面……", "name": "銀行經理"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1041_1#1$1"}, {"id": 42, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 43, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 44, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "啊，原來是您啊，潔西卡小姐。", "name": "銀行經理"}}, {"id": 45, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不知這麼晚造訪，您有何貴幹？", "name": "銀行經理"}}, {"id": 46, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1034_jesca2_1#11$1"}}, {"id": 47, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "別……別趕他們走！", "name": "潔西卡"}, "figure_art": "avg_1034_jesca2_1#11$1"}, {"id": 48, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1041_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 49, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "趕他們走？我們趕誰了？", "name": "銀行經理"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1041_1#1$1"}, {"id": 50, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1034_jesca2_1#11$1"}}, {"id": 51, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那些欠債的居民，別讓黑鋼趕他們走！", "name": "潔西卡"}, "figure_art": "avg_1034_jesca2_1#11$1"}, {"id": 52, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1041_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 53, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……這是誰的意思？克里夫先生的？", "name": "銀行經理"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1041_1#1$1"}, {"id": 54, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1034_jesca2_1#11$1"}}, {"id": 55, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我的，我自己的意思！", "name": "潔西卡"}, "figure_art": "avg_1034_jesca2_1#11$1"}, {"id": 56, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1041_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 57, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我沒聽錯吧，潔西卡小姐？開玩笑也要有限度。", "name": "銀行經理"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1041_1#1$1"}, {"id": 58, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 0.3, "xstrength": 30.0, "ystrength": 30.0, "vibrato": 30.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 59, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1034_jesca2_1#11$1"}}, {"id": 60, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這不是開玩笑！如果你們要找人還債，我、我來替他們還，能不能過了冬天再讓他們離開？現在去拓荒地，是在讓他們去送死啊！", "name": "潔西卡"}, "figure_art": "avg_1034_jesca2_1#11$1"}, {"id": 61, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1041_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 62, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "在銀行，能說話的不是一個異想天開的傭兵，是實實在在的金券。", "name": "銀行經理"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1041_1#1$1"}, {"id": 63, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1034_jesca2_1#11$1"}}, {"id": 64, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "金券我有！這不是異想天開，我說了要替他們還，就會替他們還！", "name": "潔西卡"}, "figure_art": "avg_1034_jesca2_1#11$1"}, {"id": 65, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1041_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 66, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "抱歉，銀行不接待妄想症患者——", "name": "銀行經理"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1041_1#1$1"}, {"id": 67, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1034_jesca2_1#12$1"}}, {"id": 68, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 0.3, "xstrength": 30.0, "ystrength": 30.0, "vibrato": 30.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 69, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我是伯尼·布林雷的女兒，伯尼·布林雷……雷神工業的負責人兼大股東！", "name": "潔西卡"}, "figure_art": "avg_1034_jesca2_1#12$1"}, {"id": 70, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 71, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1034_jesca2_1#3$1"}}, {"id": 72, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 73, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 74, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "話才說出口，潔西卡便愣住了，自來到黑鋼後，無論面對怎樣的挫折與困難，她都不會指望自己的父親與家族。"}}, {"id": 75, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那是她一貫的堅持，她不希望她的姓氏給她帶來特殊的優待。"}}, {"id": 76, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "可在剛剛，她搬出了父親的名字，搬出了家徽上的姓氏。"}}, {"id": 77, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1041_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 78, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "伯尼·布林雷？", "name": "銀行經理"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1041_1#1$1"}, {"id": 79, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那你倒也真是位大人物了，潔西卡·布林雷小姐。", "name": "銀行經理"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1041_1#1$1"}, {"id": 80, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1034_jesca2_1#11$1"}}, {"id": 81, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你不用挖苦我，女士。告訴我吧，到底要多少錢？", "name": "潔西卡"}, "figure_art": "avg_1034_jesca2_1#11$1"}, {"id": 82, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1041_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 83, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嗯……一時間我也拿不出個確切數字，不過沒關係，西爾維婭在這裡，她一向對數字很敏感。", "name": "銀行經理"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1041_1#1$1"}, {"id": 84, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "愣著幹什麼，西爾維婭，告訴布林雷小姐啊。", "name": "銀行經理"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1041_1#1$1"}, {"id": 85, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1039_1#8$1"}}, {"id": 86, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……潔西卡小姐，我……", "name": "西爾維婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1039_1#8$1"}, {"id": 87, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1041_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 88, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "西爾維婭，她是布林雷家的孩子，對她而言那應該只是個小數字。", "name": "銀行經理"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1041_1#1$1"}, {"id": 89, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1039_1#8$1"}}, {"id": 90, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這、這樣不好……", "name": "西爾維婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1039_1#8$1"}, {"id": 91, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 0.3, "xstrength": 30.0, "ystrength": 30.0, "vibrato": 30.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 92, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1041_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 93, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "告訴她，西爾維婭！", "name": "銀行經理"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1041_1#1$1"}, {"id": 94, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1039_1#8$1"}}, {"id": 95, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "迄今為止……達維鎮所有人的債務約計……兩億七千六百萬金券，到明年春天的話，粗略算下來，一共需要償付……", "name": "西爾維婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1039_1#8$1"}, {"id": 96, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1034_jesca2_1#11$1"}}, {"id": 97, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "要多少？", "name": "潔西卡"}, "figure_art": "avg_1034_jesca2_1#11$1"}, {"id": 98, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1039_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 99, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "兩千八百四十五萬金券。", "name": "西爾維婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1039_1#2$1"}, {"id": 100, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1034_jesca2_1#3$1"}}, {"id": 101, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "兩千……八百萬？", "name": "潔西卡"}, "figure_art": "avg_1034_jesca2_1#3$1"}, {"id": 102, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1041_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 103, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這點小錢，換大家在地塊上安安穩穩多待三個月，很划算吧，布林雷小姐？", "name": "銀行經理"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1041_1#1$1"}, {"id": 104, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 105, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1034_jesca2_1#14$1"}}, {"id": 106, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 107, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 108, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1041_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 109, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "怎麼又不說話了？", "name": "銀行經理"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1041_1#1$1"}, {"id": 110, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1034_jesca2_1#11$1"}}, {"id": 111, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我、我手頭暫時沒有那麼多，但我、我可以盡量拿出來……", "name": "潔西卡"}, "figure_art": "avg_1034_jesca2_1#11$1"}, {"id": 112, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1041_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 113, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "兩千八百四十五萬……看來那些有家族信託基金的大小姐也沒辦法一次性拿出這麼多錢啊？", "name": "銀行經理"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1041_1#1$1"}, {"id": 114, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "倒也是新知識。", "name": "銀行經理"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1041_1#1$1"}, {"id": 115, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1034_jesca2_1#9$1"}}, {"id": 116, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我……我……不……", "name": "潔西卡"}, "figure_art": "avg_1034_jesca2_1#9$1"}, {"id": 117, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1039_1#8$1"}}, {"id": 118, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "潔西卡……", "name": "西爾維婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1039_1#8$1"}, {"id": 119, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1034_jesca2_1#10$1"}}, {"id": 120, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "西爾維婭，我、我……", "name": "潔西卡"}, "figure_art": "avg_1034_jesca2_1#10$1"}, {"id": 121, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1039_1#8$1"}}, {"id": 122, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你……不是達維鎮的人，為大家做到這個地步……真的沒有必要。", "name": "西爾維婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1039_1#8$1"}, {"id": 123, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "潔西卡，聽我說，你先回去吧……就、就算你用錢能幫這一次，那下一次、下下一次……又要怎麼辦呢？", "name": "西爾維婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1039_1#8$1"}, {"id": 124, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1034_jesca2_1#7$1", "focus": "n"}}, {"id": 125, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "潔西卡顫抖著嘴唇，一句話也說不出來。"}}, {"id": 126, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "她知道，西爾維婭並非在挖苦自己，只是在陳述事實。"}}, {"id": 127, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那串躺在她帳戶裡的數字，就算能保她一生無憂，但於這個地塊上的人而言，就連一個月的安穩也無法保障。"}}, {"id": 128, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "她想起父親曾經語重心長地提醒自己，做事要權衡利弊，要量力而為。"}}, {"id": 129, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "她學不會，所以總是一事無成。"}}, {"id": 130, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 4.0}}, {"id": 131, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 132, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 3.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 133, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 134, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 135, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "42_g9_modernoffice", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 136, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 137, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$doorknockquite", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 138, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 139, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "克里夫先生，您在嗎？", "name": "秘書"}}, {"id": 140, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1036_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 141, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "在，怎麼了？", "name": "“橋夾”克里夫"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1036_1#1$1"}, {"id": 142, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "focus": "n"}}, {"id": 143, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "克里夫先生，那個人來了，請問您方便會見嗎？", "name": "秘書"}}, {"id": 144, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1036_1#7$1"}}, {"id": 145, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "“橋夾”克里夫"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1036_1#7$1"}, {"id": 146, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "focus": "n"}}, {"id": 147, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 148, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$doorknockquite", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 149, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 150, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "克里夫先生？", "name": "秘書"}}, {"id": 151, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1036_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 152, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嗯，我聽到了，直接帶他進來吧。", "name": "“橋夾”克里夫"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1036_1#1$1"}, {"id": 153, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_glassdooropen"}}, {"id": 154, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 155, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 156, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 157, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 158, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "42_g3_diner", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 159, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 160, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_doorbell", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 161, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 162, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$storyendjp_intro", "key": "$storyendjp_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 163, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_1034_jesca2_1#9$1", "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 164, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 165, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4104_coldst_1#8$1", "duration": 0.5}}, {"id": 166, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 167, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 168, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "潔西卡？你怎麼過來了，你沒回黑鋼本艦嗎？", "name": "海倫娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_4104_coldst_1#8$1"}, {"id": 169, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_1034_jesca2_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 170, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……海倫娜女士，伍德洛先生他……回來了嗎？", "name": "潔西卡"}, "figure_art": "avg_1034_jesca2_1#1$1"}, {"id": 171, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4104_coldst_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 172, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "沒有，他說是有舊識來，得去見見，一直沒回來……", "name": "海倫娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_4104_coldst_1#1$1"}, {"id": 173, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4104_coldst_1#11$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 174, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你看著不對勁……怎麼了，伍迪他……出事了？", "name": "海倫娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_4104_coldst_1#11$1"}, {"id": 175, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_1034_jesca2_1#14$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 176, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不……他應該是去黑鋼本艦見我們的老闆了……他們有故交，說不定能讓老闆回心轉意……", "name": "潔西卡"}, "figure_art": "avg_1034_jesca2_1#14$1"}, {"id": 177, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4104_coldst_1#4$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 178, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "黑鋼老闆？他還有這麼一號朋友，從沒聽他說過啊。", "name": "海倫娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_4104_coldst_1#4$1"}, {"id": 179, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_1034_jesca2_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 180, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他不是有張照片嗎，裡面就是他倆和另外一位薩科塔……", "name": "潔西卡"}, "figure_art": "avg_1034_jesca2_1#1$1"}, {"id": 181, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4104_coldst_1#2$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 182, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那張照片？我有印象，可是一直鎖在他抽屜裡，你怎麼看見的？", "name": "海倫娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_4104_coldst_1#2$1"}, {"id": 183, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_1034_jesca2_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 184, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那……那不重要，重要的是照片上他們三個人笑得很開心，不是嗎？", "name": "潔西卡"}, "figure_art": "avg_1034_jesca2_1#1$1"}, {"id": 185, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4104_coldst_1#2$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 186, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……你確定伍迪去見照片上的人了？", "name": "海倫娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_4104_coldst_1#2$1"}, {"id": 187, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_1034_jesca2_1#16$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 188, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……您是知道些什麼，對不對？", "name": "潔西卡"}, "figure_art": "avg_1034_jesca2_1#16$1"}, {"id": 189, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4104_coldst_1#2$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 190, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "潔西卡，伍迪在獨立戰爭中的經歷，我知道的不多，那張照片上的人，我也只是簡單聽過幾句……", "name": "海倫娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_4104_coldst_1#2$1"}, {"id": 191, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4104_coldst_1#3$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 192, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "當年，就是你老闆做出的選擇，導致伍迪與另外一人被敵軍俘虜，關進了柯略斯營地。", "name": "海倫娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_4104_coldst_1#3$1"}, {"id": 193, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_1034_jesca2_1#14$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 194, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……柯略斯營地是……俘虜營？", "name": "潔西卡"}, "figure_art": "avg_1034_jesca2_1#14$1"}, {"id": 195, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4104_coldst_1#2$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 196, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你不知道嗎？也是，那麼久遠的事了，官方也不想重提，你們年輕人應該是不知道的。", "name": "海倫娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_4104_coldst_1#2$1"}, {"id": 197, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "柯略斯營地是哥倫比亞獨立戰爭時期由維多利亞軍方修建的戰俘營，在裡面……發生過駭人聽聞的虐俘事件。", "name": "海倫娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_4104_coldst_1#2$1"}, {"id": 198, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 0.3, "xstrength": 30.0, "ystrength": 30.0, "vibrato": 30.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 199, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_1034_jesca2_1#3$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 200, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "虐俘……？！", "name": "潔西卡"}, "figure_art": "avg_1034_jesca2_1#3$1"}, {"id": 201, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4104_coldst_1#5$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 202, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "是的，進去十個人，出來的卻只有一個人。", "name": "海倫娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_4104_coldst_1#5$1"}, {"id": 203, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "潔西卡，誰會把害自己陷入那種地方的人稱為故交呢……", "name": "海倫娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_4104_coldst_1#5$1"}, {"id": 204, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 205, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "潔西卡想起那張褐色的證件。"}}, {"id": 206, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "她突然意識到，那不是什麼褐色，那是血液乾涸的顏色。"}}, {"id": 207, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 208, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 209, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 210, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 211, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "bg_black", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 212, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 213, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 214, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "長官，您在嗎？", "name": "？？？"}}, {"id": 215, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "在，怎麼了？", "name": "面色陰沉的傭兵"}}, {"id": 216, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "長官，那個人來了，請問您方便會見嗎？", "name": "？？？"}}, {"id": 217, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嗯，直接帶他進來吧。", "name": "面色陰沉的傭兵"}}, {"id": 218, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 219, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n", "volume": 0.7}}, {"id": 220, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 221, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……我可以坐嗎？", "name": "面容枯槁的男子"}}, {"id": 222, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "當然。", "name": "面色陰沉的傭兵"}}, {"id": 223, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 224, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_clothmovement", "volume": 0.7}}, {"id": 225, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 226, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這裡有地方坐的，伍迪……", "name": "面色陰沉的傭兵"}}, {"id": 227, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……抱歉，這兩年習慣了在地上坐。都忘了，現在坐在椅子上並不會……挨揍。", "name": "面容枯槁的男子"}}, {"id": 228, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "面色陰沉的傭兵"}}, {"id": 229, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 230, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 231, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 232, "prop": "Image", "attributes": {"image": "42_i10", "screenadapt": "coverall", "xScale": 1.1, "yScale": 1.1}}, {"id": 233, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "1019年秋天，哥倫比亞，柯略斯營地"}}, {"id": 234, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 235, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 236, "prop": "ImageTween", "attributes": {"xScaleFrom": 1.1, "yScaleFrom": 1.1, "xScaleTo": 1.0, "yScaleTo": 1.0, "duration": 20.0}}, {"id": 237, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 3.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 238, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 239, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……你叫我來，有什麼話要說嗎？", "name": "面容枯槁的男子"}}, {"id": 240, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我以為，如果再相見，你才是那個有很多話要問的人。", "name": "面色陰沉的傭兵"}}, {"id": 241, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不，我只有一句話要問。", "name": "面容枯槁的男子"}}, {"id": 242, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "三年前，你為什麼沒來支援？", "name": "面容枯槁的男子"}}, {"id": 243, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你離開後，情況有變，右側的敵軍包圍線突然收緊，為了保存戰力，我只能放棄原有的營救計劃。", "name": "面色陰沉的傭兵"}}, {"id": 244, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……就幾句輕描淡寫的解釋？", "name": "面容枯槁的男子"}}, {"id": 245, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你制定了營救計劃，你派我去吸引敵軍的注意，最後你卻沒有去救他。", "name": "面容枯槁的男子"}}, {"id": 246, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "情勢所迫，我必須對手下的士兵負責。", "name": "面色陰沉的傭兵"}}, {"id": 247, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "別擺出那張事不關己的臉給我看！", "name": "面容枯槁的男子"}}, {"id": 248, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你為什麼那麼在意我的表情，伍迪？從一進門開始，你就緊盯著我的臉，閱讀我的表情。", "name": "面色陰沉的傭兵"}}, {"id": 249, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "什麼時候……薩科塔之間相處也需要察言觀色了。怎麼回事，伍迪？", "name": "面色陰沉的傭兵"}}, {"id": 250, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……從他去世後，這就變成習慣了，畢竟這裡除了我和他，沒有其他的薩科塔。", "name": "面容枯槁的男子"}}, {"id": 251, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他什麼時候去世的？這裡的文件上只有一個“死亡”的章印，餘下都未記錄在冊。", "name": "面色陰沉的傭兵"}}, {"id": 252, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "記不清詳細的……沒有日曆也沒有錶……大概是在去年初春……不，應該是夏天，那天我在鐵絲網外看到了一株三色堇。", "name": "面容枯槁的男子"}}, {"id": 253, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "發生什麼了……？", "name": "面色陰沉的傭兵"}}, {"id": 254, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "一開始……他燒得滾燙……不停囈語，眼睛睜得很大，緊緊拽住我的衣袖，像是有什麼要對我說。", "name": "面容枯槁的男子"}}, {"id": 255, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "於是，我湊了上去想要分辨他到底說了什麼。", "name": "面容枯槁的男子"}}, {"id": 256, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他說了什麼……", "name": "面色陰沉的傭兵"}}, {"id": 257, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我沒有聽到……他鬆開了我的袖子，眼睛依然睜著，瞳孔放大了……黑洞洞的……好像能將周圍的一切都吸入進去。", "name": "面容枯槁的男子"}}, {"id": 258, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "伍迪……", "name": "面色陰沉的傭兵"}}, {"id": 259, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "為什麼呢，為什麼……你沒有來呢？", "name": "面容枯槁的男子"}}, {"id": 260, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 261, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.6, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 262, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "男人轉過頭來，將視線重新放回到傭兵的臉上，眼神空洞。", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 263, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "他瞳孔中的黑色不停蔓延、流動、旋轉，像是要將周圍的一切吞噬殆盡。", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 264, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "在對方木然的瞪視中，傭兵覺得好像有一把不知從何處伸出的鉤子，穿過了腳踝，將自己狠狠拖拽進那片黑色的旋渦中。", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 265, "prop": "subtitle", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 266, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 267, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 3.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 268, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 269, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 270, "prop": "image", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 271, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "42_g9_modernoffice", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 272, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 273, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 274, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1036_1#1$1", "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 275, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1034_1#1$1", "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 276, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 277, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1036_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 278, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "“橋夾”克里夫"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1036_1#1$1"}, {"id": 279, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1034_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 280, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我現在該叫你什麼，你現在好像改名了？", "name": "伍德洛"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1034_1#1$1"}, {"id": 281, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1036_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 282, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "都行……我以為你會來得更早一些，伍迪。", "name": "“橋夾”克里夫"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1036_1#1$1"}, {"id": 283, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1034_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 284, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "經歷過昨夜的事，我有很多的事要忙，有很多朋友的忙要幫。", "name": "伍德洛"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1034_1#1$1"}, {"id": 285, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1036_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 286, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你如果需要幫助，用錢還是用人，都可以和我講。", "name": "“橋夾”克里夫"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1036_1#1$1"}, {"id": 287, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1034_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 288, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "謝謝，克里夫先生，不用了。來得及時才叫幫助，而你的幫助……總是姍姍來遲。", "name": "伍德洛"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1034_1#1$1"}, {"id": 289, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1036_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 290, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "是啊，什麼事情總是要合時宜的好。", "name": "“橋夾”克里夫"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1036_1#1$1"}, {"id": 291, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1034_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 292, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你來做什麼？", "name": "伍德洛"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1034_1#1$1"}, {"id": 293, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1036_1#8$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 294, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "故人相見，就不能先問句好嗎？", "name": "“橋夾”克里夫"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1036_1#8$1"}, {"id": 295, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1034_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 296, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……一個簡單的“故人”都不能概括我們的關係，你為何會覺得我們再見時會像故人一樣相處？", "name": "伍德洛"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1034_1#1$1"}, {"id": 297, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1036_1#10$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 298, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那你希望我怎樣與你相處呢，伍迪？", "name": "“橋夾”克里夫"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1036_1#10$1"}, {"id": 299, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1034_1#2$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 300, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我希望我們不用相處。", "name": "伍德洛"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1034_1#2$1"}, {"id": 301, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1036_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 302, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "伍迪，我們都是老頭子了，講話何必帶著刺。", "name": "“橋夾”克里夫"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1036_1#1$1"}, {"id": 303, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這十幾年裡，我有很多朋友，身體陸陸續續都出了問題，葬禮一場接著一場，還健在的傢伙，偶爾見一面也不容易。", "name": "“橋夾”克里夫"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1036_1#1$1"}, {"id": 304, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你住得這麼遠，我也不指望能從報紙上找到你的訃告，所以只能來親眼看看了。", "name": "“橋夾”克里夫"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1036_1#1$1"}, {"id": 305, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1034_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 306, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你不用來，要是我死了，葬禮上沒有你的位置。", "name": "伍德洛"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1034_1#1$1"}, {"id": 307, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1036_1#5$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 308, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那還真是遺憾，伍迪，很早以前我們約好會在對方的葬禮上致詞的。", "name": "“橋夾”克里夫"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1036_1#5$1"}, {"id": 309, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1034_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 310, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "如果你熱衷於此，有很多人會願意你在他們的葬禮上講些什麼，但我的……還是算了吧。", "name": "伍德洛"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1034_1#1$1"}, {"id": 311, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1036_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 312, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "伍迪，我不喜歡葬禮，我出席葬禮只是因為躺在棺槨中的人是我的朋友。", "name": "“橋夾”克里夫"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1036_1#1$1"}, {"id": 313, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1034_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 314, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "葬禮上你坐在哪裡？親朋好友中間嗎？", "name": "伍德洛"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1034_1#1$1"}, {"id": 315, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1036_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 316, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "很少，大多數情況下，如果不是親屬要求，我會站在很遠的地方旁觀整場葬禮。", "name": "“橋夾”克里夫"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1036_1#1$1"}, {"id": 317, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1034_1#10$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 318, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "怎麼，你怕承受不住他們的傷痛嗎？", "name": "伍德洛"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1034_1#10$1"}, {"id": 319, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1036_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 320, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "其他種族的葬禮上，傷痛其實是種相對私人的體驗，我猜，我們只能各自應對。", "name": "“橋夾”克里夫"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1036_1#1$1"}, {"id": 321, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1034_1#6$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 322, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "虛情假意就算了吧，我直接了當的問你，那個人我埋在了戰俘營後面的山坡上，你之後去看過嗎？", "name": "伍德洛"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1034_1#6$1"}, {"id": 323, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1036_1#7$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 324, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "“橋夾”克里夫"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1036_1#7$1"}, {"id": 325, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "很遺憾，沒有，我抽不出時間。", "name": "“橋夾”克里夫"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1036_1#7$1"}, {"id": 326, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1034_1#5$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 327, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……你還真是一點都沒變。", "name": "伍德洛"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1034_1#5$1"}, {"id": 328, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 329, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 330, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 331, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 332, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_1034_jesca2_1#9$1", "focus": "all"}}, {"id": 333, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4104_coldst_1#2$1", "focus": "all"}}, {"id": 334, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "42_g3_diner", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 335, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 336, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 337, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4104_coldst_1#2$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 338, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "可伍迪為什麼要去找他……？", "name": "海倫娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_4104_coldst_1#2$1"}, {"id": 339, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_1034_jesca2_1#9$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 340, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "怪我……我拜託他去的……", "name": "潔西卡"}, "figure_art": "avg_1034_jesca2_1#9$1"}, {"id": 341, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4104_coldst_1#8$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 342, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "潔西卡，你？！", "name": "海倫娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_4104_coldst_1#8$1"}, {"id": 343, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_1034_jesca2_1#9$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 344, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我以為……他與老闆是朋友，看在過去的情面上，老闆或許會對地塊上的大家……手下留情……", "name": "潔西卡"}, "figure_art": "avg_1034_jesca2_1#9$1"}, {"id": 345, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4104_coldst_1#8$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 346, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你怎麼天真到這份上？潔西卡……伍迪他、他……", "name": "海倫娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_4104_coldst_1#8$1"}, {"id": 347, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_1034_jesca2_1#7$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 348, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我……", "name": "潔西卡"}, "figure_art": "avg_1034_jesca2_1#7$1"}, {"id": 349, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "潔西卡"}, "figure_art": "avg_1034_jesca2_1#7$1"}, {"id": 350, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4104_coldst_1#5$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 351, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "算了，潔西卡……事到如今，我也沒必要瞞著你了。", "name": "海倫娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_4104_coldst_1#5$1"}, {"id": 352, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我打算離開地塊去拓荒地了。", "name": "海倫娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_4104_coldst_1#5$1"}, {"id": 353, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_1034_jesca2_1#10$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 354, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "連您也……", "name": "潔西卡"}, "figure_art": "avg_1034_jesca2_1#10$1"}, {"id": 355, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4104_coldst_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 356, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "是啊，老顧客們一個個都被遣送走了，剩我們幾個老傢伙，就算是保住餐廳留在地塊上，又有什麼意思呢？", "name": "海倫娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_4104_coldst_1#1$1"}, {"id": 357, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "何況昨夜一場打鬥下來，看這四處漏風的牆，我也實在是沒有心力再修補了。", "name": "海倫娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_4104_coldst_1#1$1"}, {"id": 358, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4104_coldst_1#4$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 359, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "為它付出的這些年，已經夠了……夠多了。", "name": "海倫娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_4104_coldst_1#4$1"}, {"id": 360, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_1034_jesca2_1#7$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 361, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "抱歉，抱歉……", "name": "潔西卡"}, "figure_art": "avg_1034_jesca2_1#7$1"}, {"id": 362, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4104_coldst_1#2$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 363, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "潔西卡，明明你什麼都沒做，為什麼卻總在說抱歉？", "name": "海倫娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_4104_coldst_1#2$1"}, {"id": 364, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_1034_jesca2_1#7$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 365, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "因為我什麼也沒做到，抱歉，真的……", "name": "潔西卡"}, "figure_art": "avg_1034_jesca2_1#7$1"}, {"id": 366, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4104_coldst_1#2$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 367, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你不該為這個責怪自己，地塊淪落到這一步，你一個外人是最不該為此自責的，回朋友身邊去吧……", "name": "海倫娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_4104_coldst_1#2$1"}, {"id": 368, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你將來還有自己的日子要過，沒必要為了我們這樣勞心勞力。", "name": "海倫娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_4104_coldst_1#2$1"}, {"id": 369, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "至於你當時給我的支票……你還是拿回去吧。", "name": "海倫娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_4104_coldst_1#2$1"}, {"id": 370, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_1034_jesca2_1#9$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 371, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "可……這已經是我僅剩下的能做的事情了……", "name": "潔西卡"}, "figure_art": "avg_1034_jesca2_1#9$1"}, {"id": 372, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4104_coldst_1#2$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 373, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "拿回去吧。", "name": "海倫娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_4104_coldst_1#2$1"}, {"id": 374, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_1034_jesca2_1#9$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 375, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……海倫娜女士，那你們準備什麼時候離開？", "name": "潔西卡"}, "figure_art": "avg_1034_jesca2_1#9$1"}, {"id": 376, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4104_coldst_1#3$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 377, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "還不急，我想，離開前怎麼也得好好告別一番。", "name": "海倫娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_4104_coldst_1#3$1"}, {"id": 378, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 379, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 380, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 381, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "42_g1_mine", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 382, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 383, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 384, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "合上餐廳門，潔西卡呆呆地靜立在門前，支票在她的手心裡被緊緊捏成一團。"}}, {"id": 385, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "她突然狠狠踢向路邊的積雪，揚起的雪粒灑在頭頂，髮絲被雪粒沁濕搭在額邊，讓她發燙的額頭稍稍降低了溫度……"}}, {"id": 386, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "她從包裡拿出錄音機，開始倒帶，從頭開始播放那段已經聽過無數遍的錄音。"}}, {"id": 387, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 388, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.6, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 389, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "“……不過是個不知輕重的大小姐罷了，你還能做什麼呢？”", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 390, "prop": "subtitle", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 391, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 392, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "她一邊這麼想著，一邊緩緩向黑色的巨艦走去。"}}, {"id": 393, "prop": "MusicVolume", "attributes": {"volume": 0.2, "fadetime": 5.0}}, {"id": 394, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 395, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 396, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 397, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 398, "prop": "CameraEffect", "attributes": {"effect": "Grayscale", "fadetime": 0.0, "keep": "true", "initamount": 0.0, "amount": 0.7, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 399, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "bg_aircraft_2", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 400, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 401, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 402, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$transmission"}}, {"id": 403, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 404, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "有人聽到嗎？", "name": "？？？"}}, {"id": 405, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "救救我們……那些、那些薩卡茲突然登上地塊……", "name": "？？？"}}, {"id": 406, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_windowbreak", "volume": 0.2}}, {"id": 407, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "很多人死了，我和剩下的人躲在市政廳的地下室中……嗶滋……嗶滋……", "name": "？？？"}}, {"id": 408, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們試著聯繫了倫蒂尼姆的駐軍……", "name": "？？？"}}, {"id": 409, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但沒人回覆我們……沒有任何人回覆我們……", "name": "？？？"}}, {"id": 410, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_paniccrowd", "volume": 0.2}}, {"id": 411, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "無論是誰，如果你能收到這段通訊訊息，求你，幫幫我們……", "name": "？？？"}}, {"id": 412, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你是我們唯一的希望了……", "name": "？？？"}}, {"id": 413, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_collapse", "volume": 0.3}}, {"id": 414, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嗶滋……嗶滋……", "name": "？？？"}}, {"id": 415, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 416, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$transmission"}}, {"id": 417, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 418, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 419, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "為什麼我要做傭兵呢？"}}, {"id": 420, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我既救不了別人的生命，也救不了別人的生活。"}}, {"id": 421, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 422, "prop": "Stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 423, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 424, "prop": "CameraEffect", "attributes": {"effect": "Grayscale", "fadetime": 0.0, "amount": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 425, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 426, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "42_g10_blacksteelarmory", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 427, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 428, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$dooropenquite"}}, {"id": 429, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1034_jesca2_1#7$1", "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 430, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 431, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_106_franka_1#5$1"}}, {"id": 432, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "潔西卡，你今天一天都去哪裡啦？聯繫也聯繫不上。", "name": "芙蘭卡"}, "figure_art": "avg_106_franka_1#5$1"}, {"id": 433, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1034_jesca2_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 434, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我去了……沒事，我就是四處走了走。", "name": "潔西卡"}, "figure_art": "avg_1034_jesca2_1#1$1"}, {"id": 435, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_107_liskam_1#8$1"}}, {"id": 436, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "到底怎麼了？", "name": "雷蛇"}, "figure_art": "avg_107_liskam_1#8$1"}, {"id": 437, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1034_jesca2_1#9$1"}}, {"id": 438, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$dignified_intro", "key": "$dignified_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 439, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "隊長，我真的……我……已經完全搞不懂這次任務的意義在哪裡了。", "name": "潔西卡"}, "figure_art": "avg_1034_jesca2_1#9$1"}, {"id": 440, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_106_franka_1#11$1"}}, {"id": 441, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "潔西卡……你是看到了什麼嗎？", "name": "芙蘭卡"}, "figure_art": "avg_106_franka_1#11$1"}, {"id": 442, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1034_jesca2_1#9$1"}}, {"id": 443, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……我看到我們的同事將負債的居民從他們的房子裡帶走，然後送上去往拓荒地的車隊。", "name": "潔西卡"}, "figure_art": "avg_1034_jesca2_1#9$1"}, {"id": 444, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_106_franka_1#5$1"}}, {"id": 445, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "什麼？", "name": "芙蘭卡"}, "figure_art": "avg_106_franka_1#5$1"}, {"id": 446, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_107_liskam_1#3$1"}}, {"id": 447, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "雷蛇"}, "figure_art": "avg_107_liskam_1#3$1"}, {"id": 448, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_106_franka_1#8$1"}}, {"id": 449, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "喂，優等生，你別光顧著看通訊器啊！", "name": "芙蘭卡"}, "figure_art": "avg_106_franka_1#8$1"}, {"id": 450, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你聽到潔西卡說的了嗎？！", "name": "芙蘭卡"}, "figure_art": "avg_106_franka_1#8$1"}, {"id": 451, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_107_liskam_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 452, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "聽到了……而且我還有條比那更荒唐的消息。", "name": "雷蛇"}, "figure_art": "avg_107_liskam_1#1$1"}, {"id": 453, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_107_liskam_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 454, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "上級指令，之後銀行的保衛工作交由我們負責，需要二十四小時守衛在外，具體輪班計劃由我們自己安排。", "name": "雷蛇"}, "figure_art": "avg_107_liskam_1#2$1"}, {"id": 455, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 0.3, "xstrength": 30.0, "ystrength": 30.0, "vibrato": 30.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 456, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_106_franka_1#6$1"}}, {"id": 457, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "什麼……給銀行做保安？！", "name": "芙蘭卡"}, "figure_art": "avg_106_franka_1#6$1"}, {"id": 458, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_107_liskam_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 459, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "沒錯。", "name": "雷蛇"}, "figure_art": "avg_107_liskam_1#1$1"}, {"id": 460, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1034_jesca2_1#10$1"}}, {"id": 461, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "潔西卡"}, "figure_art": "avg_1034_jesca2_1#10$1"}, {"id": 462, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1034_jesca2_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 463, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "呵……", "name": "潔西卡"}, "figure_art": "avg_1034_jesca2_1#2$1"}, {"id": 464, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1034_jesca2_1#15$1"}}, {"id": 465, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……真是……他媽的……可笑……", "name": "潔西卡"}, "figure_art": "avg_1034_jesca2_1#15$1"}, {"id": 466, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_107_liskam_1#8$1"}}, {"id": 467, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "潔西卡，你……", "name": "雷蛇"}, "figure_art": "avg_107_liskam_1#8$1"}, {"id": 468, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 469, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 470, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 3.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 471, "prop": "Image", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 472, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 473, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 474, "prop": "Image", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 475, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": ""}}], "OPTIONTRACE": true}